<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 32 32'><circle cx='16' cy='16' r='16' fill='%23dc2626'/><text x='16' y='21' text-anchor='middle' font-size='13' font-weight='800' fill='white' font-family='Arial'>If</text></svg>">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: #0f172a; background: #f8fafc; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 24px; }
    .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.08); padding: 48px 40px; width: 100%; max-width: 500px; text-align: center; }
    .icon-wrap { width: 72px; height: 72px; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 24px; }
    .icon-wrap svg { width: 36px; height: 36px; color: #16a34a; }
    h1 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    p  { font-size: 15px; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .cred-box { background: #f1f5f9; border: 1.5px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 10px; padding: 18px 22px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: left; }
    .cred-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-size: 14px; }
    .cred-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .cred-label { color: #64748b; font-weight: 600; }
    .cred-value { font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 600; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; background: #fef2f2; color: #dc2626; border: 1px solid #fca5a5; border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 10px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #dc2626; color: #fff; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; margin-top: 8px; transition: background .15s; }
    .btn:hover { background: #b91c1c; text-decoration: none; }
    .warning { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: #92400e; margin: 16px 0; text-align: left; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">

    <% if (alreadyActive) { %>
      <div class="icon-wrap" style="background:#eff6ff;">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="#1d4ed8">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1>Demo bereits aktiviert</h1>
      <p>Ihr Demo-Zugang ist bereits aktiv. Melden Sie sich mit Ihren bestehenden Zugangsdaten an.</p>
      <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="btn">Zum Login</a>

    <% } else { %>
      <div class="icon-wrap">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1>Demo aktiviert! <span class="badge">DEMO</span></h1>
      <p>Hallo <strong><%= name %></strong>, Ihr 14-Tage-Demo-Zugang ist jetzt aktiv.</p>
      <p>Ihre Zugangsdaten wurden auch per E-Mail an <strong><%= email %></strong> gesendet.</p>

      <div class="cred-box">
        <div class="cred-row">
          <span class="cred-label">E-Mail</span>
          <span class="cred-value"><%= email %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="cred-row">
          <span class="cred-label">Passwort</span>
          <span class="cred-value"><%= password %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="cred-row">
          <span class="cred-label">Unterweisungen</span>
          <span class="cred-value"><%= trainingCount %> Demo-Unterweisungen</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cred-row">
          <span class="cred-label">Gültig bis</span>
          <span class="cred-value"><%= new Date(expiresAt).toLocaleDateString('de-DE', {day:'2-digit',month:'2-digit',year:'numeric'}) %></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="warning">
        Bitte notieren Sie das Passwort – es wird aus Sicherheitsgründen nicht erneut angezeigt. Ändern Sie es nach dem ersten Login unter "Passwort ändern".
      </div>

      <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="btn">Jetzt anmelden →</a>

      <p style="margin-top:20px;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8;">
        Fragen? <a href="mailto:info@ifdau.de" style="color:#dc2626;">info@ifdau.de</a>
      </p>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
